    "name": "May De Ville Lakeside Hotel",
    "detail": "this hotel is by far the best of the several we have tried in the old quarter over the past couple years. the location is perfect for wandering around the lake and the surrounding area. i can't say enough about the staff; their friendliness and efforts to please us were amazing. the honeymoon suite on the 7th floor is massive compared to the rooms usually available in the price range. sitting out on the balcony at sunset, just high enough above the street noise, offered a great view to relax and enjoy a cold drink. the front desk staff booked our necessary onward travel and hired the taxi at cheaper rates than out on the street. we had a delightful stay at the may de ville old quarter hotel in hanoi.",
